OL,3,CMel B awarded honorary doctorate for
OL,4,Cdomestic abuse campaigning
OL,6,FThe singer, also known as Mel B and
OL,7,FScary Spice, has been given the award
OL,8,Ffrom Leeds Beckett University in
OL,9,Frecognition of her work advocating for
OL,10,Fdomestic abuse victims.
OL,12,FIn a speech given through tears, Brown
OL,13,Faddressed the crowd: "I can perform on
OL,14,FWembley Stadium but being here in
OL,15,Ffront of all of you is really nerve-
OL,16,Fwracking.
OL,18,F"I can't be more thankful for this
OL,19,Fopportunity and more grateful to be
OL,20,Freceiving this. I can't really even
OL,21,Ftalk so thank you."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
