OL,3,CMel B awarded honorary doctorate for
OL,4,Cdomestic abuse campaigning
OL,6,FBrown has been an advocate for
OL,7,Fdomestic abuse victims since she made
OL,8,Fclaims in her 2018 memoir Brutally
OL,9,FHonest that she had suffered abuse
OL,10,Ffrom her ex-husband Stephen Belafonte,
OL,11,Fallegations he has repeatedly denied.
OL,13,FSpeaking to ITV News Arts Editor Nina
OL,14,FNannar, she said: "It's surreal to be
OL,15,Fhonest and I feel really nervous and
OL,16,Fshy, but also really proud.
OL,18,F"It started off with a not very good
OL,19,Fjourney and understanding of where I'd
OL,20,Fcome from but it's blossomed into
OL,21,Fsomething really worthwhile."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
