OL,3,CMel B awarded honorary doctorate for
OL,4,Cdomestic abuse campaigning
OL,6,FShe added that her experiences and
OL,7,Fsubsequent campaign gave her a "more
OL,8,Fimportant mission in life".
OL,10,FIn addition to her honorary doctorate,
OL,11,FBrown also completed a graduate course
OL,12,Fin Trauma Care at the university.
OL,14,F"I can't just be given a doctorate
OL,15,Fwithout going to college and studying,
OL,16,FI want to earn it too," she added.
